#Per Henrik Lausten
## Bio
Per Henrik Lausten is an independent web developer with his own one-man company in Denmark. He builds solutions for web, tablets and mobile primarily using Java and Javascript.

## Current roles
Web developer at [PHL Consult](http://PHL-Consult.dk).
Web developer at [Sherlock Web](http://www.sherlock.dk).
Web developer at [fmcg solutions](http://www.fmcgsolutions.dk).

## Blog
Per Henrik Lausten blogs at [per.lausten.dk/blog](http://per.lausten.dk/blog/).
